comments.body:
The proposed changes (namely throwing {{IOException}} from {{setDefaultUri}} method) will break other parts of Hadoop. E.g. in MR MiniMRCluster
{noformat}
342:     FileSystem.setDefaultUri(result, namenode);
{noformat}

will surely fail because now {{IOException}} has to be caught. So, the patch has to, at very least, address such issues. I'll link MAPREDUCE-1297 with this JIRA for tracking purposes.
